client.name: CreatorClient
client.description: APIs for managing aliases in Azure Maps.

credential.description: Credential needed for the client to connect to Azure.

client_id.description: Specifies which account is intended for usage in conjunction with the Azure AD security model.  It represents a unique ID for the Azure Maps account and can be retrieved from the Azure Maps management  plane Account API. To use Azure AD security in Azure Maps see the following `articles <https://aka.ms/amauthdetails>`_ for guidance.

geography.description: This parameter specifies where the Azure Maps Creator resource is located.  Valid values are us and eu.
